snippet.title: Pineapple Express - Interviews with Seth Rogen and James Franco and Danny McBride
snippet.description:
We met up for some exclusive interviews with Seth Rogen, James Franco, Danny McBride, Judd Apatow and Amber Heard for a very funny conversation about this highflying adventure.
